# ğŸ‘¤ PERSON 4 â€” Audit Logs

### `AuditLog.java`

```java
import java.time.LocalDateTime;

public class AuditLog {
    public String userId;
    public String word;
    public Action action;
    public LocalDateTime timestamp;

    public AuditLog(String userId, String word, Action action) {
        this.userId = userId;
        this.word = word;
        this.action = action;
        this.timestamp = LocalDateTime.now();
    }
}
```

