# ğŸ”¹ MAIN COORDINATOR â€” Moderation Service

### `ModerationResult.java`

```java
public class ModerationResult {
    public Action action;
    public String message;

    public ModerationResult(Action action, String message) {
        this.action = action;
        this.message = message;
    }
}
```

### `ModerationService.java`

```java
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;

public class ModerationService {

    private SeverityEngine severityEngine = new SeverityEngine();
    private TextMatcher textMatcher = new TextMatcher();
    private StrikeManager strikeManager = new StrikeManager();
    private ContextRuleEngine contextEngine = new ContextRuleEngine();

    public List<AuditLog> logs = new ArrayList<>();

    public ModerationResult moderate(
            String userId,
            String text,
            String badWord,
            Severity severity,
            String context) {

        if (!textMatcher.containsBadWord(text, badWord)) {
            return new ModerationResult(Action.ALLOW, "Clean content");
        }

        if (contextEngine.isAllowedInContext(context, severity)) {
            return new ModerationResult(Action.ALLOW, "Allowed due to context");
        }

        Action baseAction = severityEngine.decideAction(severity);
        Action finalAction = strikeManager.applyStrike(userId, baseAction);

        logs.add(new AuditLog(userId, badWord, finalAction));

        return new ModerationResult(finalAction, "Violation detected");
    }
}
```

